						<div class="postbody">My main complaint with ZIP'ed ROMs is because the NES is a computer itself, it seems counter-productive to use a format that the system itself can't work with.
<br />
<br />Things that could be part of the header/database:
<br />ROM hash
<br />filename
<br />date (if known)
<br />revision
<br />board name/number
<br />mapper name/number
<br />iNES header</div>

